    <title>Collections of problems and skills in learning Java</title>
    <url>/2021/12/30/collection-problems-skills/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Mac"><a href="#Mac" class="headerlink" title="Mac"></a>Mac</h1><h2 id="Terminal"><a href="#Terminal" class="headerlink" title="Terminal"></a>Terminal</h2><p>创建多级文件夹</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo mkdir -p a/b/c</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="其他"><a href="#其他" class="headerlink" title="其他"></a>其他</h2><p>command +·（niz的M键）同一软件内切换不同窗口</p>
<h1 id="Java"><a href="#Java" class="headerlink" title="Java"></a>Java</h1><p>查看JDK安装路径</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/usr/libexec/java_home -V</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>查看安装了哪些版本的JDK</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ls /Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>卸载对应版本的JDK</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo rm -rf /Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.7.0_79.jdk</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="环境变量配置"><a href="#环境变量配置" class="headerlink" title="环境变量配置"></a>环境变量配置</h2><p><a href="https://juejin.cn/post/6844903878694010893">https://juejin.cn/post/6844903878694010893</a></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">JAVA_HOME=/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk-11.jdk/Contents/Home</span><br><span class="line">PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH:.</span><br><span class="line">CLASSPATH=$JAVA_HOME/lib/tools.jar:$JAVA_HOME/lib/dt.jar:.</span><br><span class="line">export JAVA_HOME</span><br><span class="line">export PATH</span><br><span class="line">export CLASSPATH</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>





<h1 id="Tomcat"><a href="#Tomcat" class="headerlink" title="Tomcat"></a>Tomcat</h1><p>查询占用1099端口进程：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo lsof -i tcp:1099;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>杀掉占用端口进程（PID为查询到的进程PID）：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo kill -9 PID;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>命令行启动</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">startup.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>命令行停止</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">shutdown.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>注意：Mac在terminal启动tomcat后，会出现idea无法连接tomcat的问题，此时需要从terminal结束tomcat的进程。</p>
<p>Tomcat配置SSL</p>
<p>MacOS在访问Servlet时遇到的问题：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>This site can’t provide a secure connection</p>
<p>localhost sent an invalid response.<br>ERR_SSL_PROTOCOL_ERROR</p>
</blockquote>
<p>keytool -genkey -alias zhuzhiqiang -keyalg RSA -keystore /Users/anyware/Documents/mine/key/tomcat/zhuzhiqiangkey  </p>
<p>Tomcat 配置https mac版</p>
<p>说明：<br>生成密码：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">keytool -genkey -alias tomcatkey -keyalg RSA -keystore /Users/raywei/Library/tomcatkey/tomcatkey</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>删除密码</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">keytool -delete -alias tomcatkey -keystore /Users/raywei/Library/tomcatkey/tomcatkey</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>keystore Password: tomcatkey</p>
<p>tomcat key: tomcatkeyssl</p>
<p>导出证书：</p>
<p>keytool -export -alias tomcatkey -keystore  /Users/raywei/Library/tomcatkey/tomcatkey -file  /Users/raywei/Library/tomcatkey/tomcatkey.cer</p>
<p>导入证书</p>
<p>sudo keytool -import -trustcacerts -alias tomcatkey -keystore /Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.8.0_301.jdk/Contents/Home/jre/lib/security/cacerts -file /Users/raywei/Library/tomcatkey/tomcatkey.cer -storepass changeit</p>
<p>keytool -import -trustcacerts -alias tomcatkey /Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.8.0_301.jdk/Contents/Home/jre/lib/security/cacerts” -file /Users/raywei/Documents/tomcatkey/mycerts.cer</p>
<p>sudo keytool -delete -alias tomcatkey -keystore “/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.8.0_301.jdk/Contents/Home/jre/lib/security/cacerts” -storepass changeit</p>
<p>说明:<br>keytool -export -file “filename.crt文件地址” -alias “别名(第一步设置的)” -keystore “上一步生成的keystore地址”</p>
<p>&lt;Connector port=”8443” protocol=”org.apache.coyote.http11.Http11Protocol”  </p>
<p>SSLEnable=”true” maxThreads=”150” scheme=”https” secure=”true” clientAuth=”false” sslProtocol=”TLS” keystoreFile=”/Users/raywei/Library/tomcatkey/tomcatkey” keystorePass=”tomcatkey”/&gt;</p>
<h1 id="IDEA"><a href="#IDEA" class="headerlink" title="IDEA"></a>IDEA</h1><p>不要在Module里创建Module，但是可以在project里创建多个module。</p>
<h2 id="Short-keys"><a href="#Short-keys" class="headerlink" title="Short keys"></a>Short keys</h2><p>inn: if not null</p>
<p>ifn: if null</p>
<p>psvm: 快速生成main方法</p>
<p>sout / soutv / soutc</p>
<p>数组.for  数组.fori / itar 遍历数组</p>
<h2 id="Shortcuts"><a href="#Shortcuts" class="headerlink" title="Shortcuts"></a>Shortcuts</h2><p>智能提示： alt + enter</p>
<p>新建快捷键：鼠标放在package名上，command+n </p>
<p>从编写文档框中返回左边的project框中：command+f1</p>
<p>编译窗口switcher：control+tab</p>
<p>自动补全函数括号、分号、当前行缩进： command+shift+enter</p>
<p>自动补全变量：option+enter</p>
