<thead>
<tr>
<th>mac</th>
<th>win</th>
<th>功能</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>command+option+L</td>
<td>Ctrl+Alt+L</td>
<td>格式化代码 自动对齐代码格式</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>command +d</td>
<td>Ctrl + d</td>
<td>复制并在该行后粘贴代码</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>command +x</td>
<td>Ctrl +x</td>
<td>剪切行</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>command +v</td>
<td>Ctrl + v</td>
<td>粘贴行</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>command + Backspace</td>
<td>Ctrl + Backspace</td>
<td>删除行</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>command +/</td>
<td>Ctrl + /</td>
<td>添加或去除单行注释</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>command + option + /</td>
<td></td>
<td>Comment with Block Comment</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>shift+F6</td>
<td>shift+F6</td>
<td>重命名类或变量</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>shift+Alt+↑</td>
<td>shift+Alt+↑</td>
<td>向上移动当前行代码</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>shift+Alt+↓</td>
<td>shift+Alt+↓</td>
<td>向下移动当前行代码</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>shift+enter</td>
<td>shift+enter</td>
<td>即使光标在行的中间，也能直接去下一行开始继续输入</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td></td>
<td>Ctrl+n</td>
